      • drawWave

        public static void drawWave​(Graphics g,
                            int xStart,
                            int xEnd,
                            int y)
        Painting wave line using specified graphics. xStart parameter should be less or equals xEnd parameter.
        Parameters:
        g - Graphics to paint the wave
        xStart - x-coordinate of the start of wave line
        xEnd - x-coordinate of the end of wave line
        y - y-coordinate of the top edge of the wave line
        Throws:
        IllegalArgumentException - if xStart value is bigger than xEnd
